{"tid":2399830,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"駐港解放軍發新春賀稿　稱來年繼續維護國家主權和安全","createTime":"2021-02-08T12:33:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-08T15:58:29.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"77255c8a78c393e0ebeddfc38a88705ac2bfc254","tid":2399830,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T12:33:41.000Z","msg":"駐港解放軍司令員陳道祥、政治委員蔡永中向香港市民發新春賀稿。<br />\n<br />\n提到過去一年，國安法實施，特區政府致力於社會由亂及治，而對一國兩制和基本法全面準確貫徹落實，有了更廣泛的社會共識，對駐軍來說亦極不平凡，一手要抓疫情防控，一手要練兵備戰，完成履行防務為中心的各項任務。<br />\n<br />\n駐軍新一年會堅決貫徹黨中央的決策指示，堅決維護國家主權、安全和發展利益，為維護香港長期繁榮穩定作出新的更大貢獻。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=423439\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D423439&d=wuzGI5SyrIdJ%2FUQuqXTUiuBrFmK%2FfjgW9YhWFGnkYF4%3D&h=d1c905bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D423439&h=4d14512e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=423439</a>"},{"pid":"9082ed738276eb768f489e415ee151342e65b268","tid":2399830,"uid":251732,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T12:34:31.000Z","msg":"NMSL"},{"pid":"5b6284d574b9114649316850fc3d9084ad4fe5bf","tid":2399830,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T12:36:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"139c00d93f7fcd3b9aada67a6023609c83871861","tid":2399830,"uid":113065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-08T12:47:22.000Z","msg":"2020年前武統台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d369baab3fd3833e1d647724cb29930a9d1cd10e","tid":2399830,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc